Boulder Nature Guides Day Planner

Here are some questions to help guide you as you plan a day trip in the City of Boulder.

What time do we leave from home?

When do we fill up our gas tank for the trip?

What is our budget for this trip?

What is our plan for lunch? Do we pack lunch or purchase it?

What trails do we want to hike?

Make sure to have our map handy for you to keep track of which trails to visit!

What supplies do we need to pack?

What time do we need to be home tonight?

What is our plan for dinner?


